         <abstract>
            <p>Collection of prayers, which were used as <term key="Magic">magic prayers</term>, each of which beginning with 
               <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኦእግዚኦ፡ እግዚኦ፡</foreign> and often continued with 
               <foreign xml:lang="gez">አነኒ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በዝንቱ፡ ዘዚአከ፡ አስማት፡</foreign> or
               <foreign xml:lang="gez">አነኒ፡ ተማኅፀንኩ፡ በዝንቱ፡ ስምከ፡</foreign> and with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾasmāt</foreign>, 
               some of which are styled according to the Syriac alphabet.</p>
         </abstract>
